The Story Of My Life

Hello, I am originally from South Korea but i am half Korean and Filipino. Therefore, i had to fly back and forth from Korea to Phillippines to visit my family and attend all the schools in both countries. Living in both of those countries was fun and exciting as i had a lot of friends and was doing well in those schools. However, when i was 11, i was announced by my mom that i had to move to U.K as she was married to a British man.

) } export default SinglePost
